PROJECT NAME: CampusLoop

PROJECT TYPE:
Student Marketplace & Real-Time Communication Platform

IMPORTANT:

Build ONLY the backend system.

Frontend already exists separately.

Do NOT generate frontend pages.
Do NOT generate frontend components.
Do NOT generate UI logic.

Build a production-ready Laravel backend with MySQL, Socket.IO integration support, AI provider management, API key rotation, moderation workflows, and RBAC.

