---

API KEY ROTATION ENGINE

CRITICAL FEATURE

Requirement:

Multiple API keys per provider.

Example:

Groq Key 1
Groq Key 2
Groq Key 3

When:

* Rate Limited
* Quota Exceeded
* Timeout
* Provider Failure

Automatically:

Switch To Next Active Key

Workflow:

Request
↓
Provider Manager
↓
Current Key
↓
Failure
↓
Next Key
↓
Continue

Implement:

ProviderManagerService

ApiKeyRotationService

Provider Drivers

GroqProvider

GeminiProvider

OpenAIProvider

ClaudeProvider

---

API KEY SECURITY

Never store plain text.

Encrypt:

Crypt::encryptString()

Decrypt only when used.

Log:

* Requests
* Successes
* Failures
* Last Used
* Error Codes

